    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/b2dc1d098c476aaae7fd689eadbdd8ac.avif?t=1770918435\" width=617 height=113 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/f7e1e5ee39e15f84f2e8d9231ff73536.poster.avif?t=1770918435\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/f7e1e5ee39e15f84f2e8d9231ff73536.webm?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/f7e1e5ee39e15f84f2e8d9231ff73536.mp4?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《波提：字节国度大冒险 (Boti: Byteland Overclocked)》将创新融入至经典的3D平台游戏。在鲜活的关卡中进行二段跳、冲刺、浮空及滑行，探索由电脑及科技精华启发的美妙连击操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/7080d9110d8a9cf95f322afbcebb817b.avif?t=1770918435\" width=617 height=114 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/0a42097c084deb861fad75b600a7b855.poster.avif?t=1770918435\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/0a42097c084deb861fad75b600a7b855.webm?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/0a42097c084deb861fad75b600a7b855.mp4?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在可随时进退游戏的合作模式下，你可以和好友一起享受游戏纯粹的乐趣。本游戏可以丝滑衔接单人及双人分屏模式，和一名朋友一起冒险并拯救字节国度吧！所有的事情，一起玩，才更好玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/43032a7e4b1d89eda150bc2bce5ecbf7.avif?t=1770918435\" width=617 height=107 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/05d1e02ad12ca2a78322d6267071696c.poster.avif?t=1770918435\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/05d1e02ad12ca2a78322d6267071696c.webm?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/05d1e02ad12ca2a78322d6267071696c.mp4?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>波提是一个可爱的数据机器人，他还有两个有趣的伙伴，零号 和 壹号。和他们一起进行奇幻冒险，帮助字节国度摆脱bugs、病毒及故障的困扰吧。他们三人可爱搞怪的对话会让你开怀大笑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/8b9fced3122419bd2570df3518fc84e9.avif?t=1770918435\" width=617 height=99 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/de334a8426aa608defb24120542f831c.poster.avif?t=1770918435\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/de334a8426aa608defb24120542f831c.webm?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/de334a8426aa608defb24120542f831c.mp4?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在经典平台游戏中体验巧妙的反转。掌握充满创意的街机元素，比如跟随节奏的音乐跑酷和磁力游戏玩法，将带给你前所未有的探索及挑战体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/f6d0b673216fc5efe7cb7188c64f1aa3.avif?t=1770918435\" width=617 height=107 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/942c9300ea5a583a67252d13ce0fed77.poster.avif?t=1770918435\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161050/extras/942c9300ea5a583a67252d13ce0fed77.webm?t=1770918435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>进入字节国度，探索这个以计算机和新老技术为灵感的数字世界的秘密！这里有超多的可收集品和数据，可供你在波提的奇“技”世界中汇集并运送到合适的位置！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >波提：字节国度大冒险 官方QQ群：820304171</p>",
